        "title": "Extreme Web Performance - RSJS 2012",
        "categories": ["JavaScript", "Palestras", "Performance", "RSJS"],
        "content": "<p>Slides da minha palestra sobre Web Performance:  </p>\n<script async class=\"speakerdeck-embed\" data-id=\"3acfaf60dcbf013100ef36ab2b38a31a\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333333333\" src=\"//speakerdeck.com/assets/embed.js\"></script>",
